data.description: Inquire about sellers assumable VA loan at 2.375% interest rate. Welcome to this charming 4 bed, 2 bath brick home nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac. Step inside to discover a modern haven featuring custom cabinets, stunning quartz countertops, and stylish vinyl plank flooring throughout (carpet in bedrooms). The open kitchen seamlessly connects to the inviting living room, offering a perfect space for gatherings. The master bedroom is spacious with an ensuite and large walk in closet. A newly added paver pathway leading to a 12X12 patio complements the backyard. It is large enough to fit all of your outdoor furniture on while strategically positioned to maximize enjoyment of the rest of the back yard, making it a perfect template to a serene outdoor oasis. With a newer build and fresh paint, this home exudes both elegance and comfort, making it an ideal choice for modern living. No HOA and a short drive to grocery stores, shopping, and restaurants.
